  "text": "Six of the eight ORFs were identi¢ed in both MC58 and Z2491, with homologies between the corresponding ORFs ranging from 85 to 98% sequence identity at the amino acid level ( Table 2 ). The highest identity was found between the ORFs encoding the IgA1 protease [CITATION_1] . They both were 73% identical to the IgA1 protease of N. gonorrhoeae, the ¢rst autotransporter described in detail [CITATION_2] .",
